<p><strong>Congratulations on making it to the end.</strong></p>

<p>Tada! You have successfully updated your first Abg font thumbnail. If you’d like to see your font directory organized so that font styles are grouped in the same family, click on the tutorial for <a href="/font-names">font names</a>.</p>

<p>I hope this tutorial has been of assistance and you can put some of the information to good use when using Fontforge.<br />
<img src="/assets/images/thumbnail/20-change-abg-font-thumbnail.png" alt="finished-picture-of-abg-font-thumbnail" width="15%" height="15%" /></p>

